[l] Die gute Nachricht: Hamas akzeptiert den Palestinenserstaat in den Grenzen von 1967.Die schlechte Nachricht: Damit bricht Israels Narrativ voellig in sich zusammen, dass Hamas die fiesen Moerderterroristen sind. Was also tun? Na klar!Israeli officials rejected the document before it was made official, calling it an attempt by Hamas to trick the world into believing it was becoming a more moderate group."Hamas is attempting to fool the world but it will not succeed," said David Keyes, a spokesman for Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu's office.Oh ach so. Na dann. (Danke, Yehudit)
